{"tid":2110319,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(688981.SH) 中芯A股 今日掛牌","createTime":"2020-07-15T23:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T01:30:31.000Z","uid":131728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff85c4406eb66628c38e9dda5fd1f87594cd1ee","tid":2110319,"uid":131728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T23:43:24.000Z","msg":"抽又抽唔到<br />\n有無人會想係街貨執下死雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//中芯國際A股(688981.SH)公布，將於周四(16日)在上海科創板掛牌，上市價此前已定為每股27.46元人民幣(下同)，募資金額達453億元，自2010年以來A股最大規模的新股。<br />\n中芯A股上市首5個交易日將不設升跌幅限制，但設臨時停牌機制，當盤中交易價較開市價上漲或下跌幅度首次達到30%或60%時，會觸發一次臨時停牌。單次盤中臨時停牌的持續時間為10分鐘，每個交易日單漲跌方向只能觸發兩次臨時停牌。首掛5日之後，每日漲跌幅限制則為20%。//"},{"pid":"345bf98ab347b895cfe6e6405ab251d003b17521","tid":2110319,"uid":131728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e73e74da2a1706bea4e09881c5982211edd2d57","tid":2110319,"uid":22585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"上左，炒完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f6de877aadc0850da4e3790f26eecf1ad16dd7","tid":2110319,"uid":26367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:22:20.000Z","msg":"買A 股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040d7b9f2ffbafa117ffddb41033f003e3cfc576","tid":2110319,"uid":131728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T00:37:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://力接中芯.Hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8A%9B%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%AD%E8%8A%AF.Hk&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n360J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%